"title": "5296: disabilities",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5296: disabilities",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Physical incapacities resulting from physical or spiritual causes.</p>\n<h2>Examples of disabilities</h2>\n<h3>Barrenness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:30\">GEN 11:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">GEN 25:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:12\">MAT 19:12</a></p>\n<h3>Blindness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:30\">MAT 15:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30\">MAT 20:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:22\">MRK 8:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1\">JHN 9:1</a></p>\n<h3>Deafness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:13\">PSA 38:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:32\">MRK 7:32</a></p>\n<h3>Muteness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:13\">PSA 38:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:14\">LUK 11:14</a></p>\n<h3>Lameness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:18\">LEV 21:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:6\">2SA 5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:31\">MAT 15:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:14\">MAT 21:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:8\">ACT 14:8</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of disabilities</h2>\n<h3>God's judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:28\">DEU 28:28</a></p>\n<h3>Accident</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:4\">2SA 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>Old age</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:1\">GEN 27:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:15\">1SA 4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:35\">2SA 19:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:9\">PSA 71:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:3-Eccl12:4\">ECC 12:3–12:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:4\">ZEC 8:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:21\">HEB 11:21</a></p>\n<h3>Congenital defects</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:12\">MAT 19:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1\">JHN 9:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:8\">ACT 14:8</a></p>\n<h3>Cruelty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:6-Judg1:7\">JDG 1:6–1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:2\">1SA 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:7\">2KI 25:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:25\">EZK 23:25</a></p>\n<h3>Illness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:23\">1KI 15:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:12\">2CH 16:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:13-Gal4:15\">GAL 4:13–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Acts of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:11\">GEN 19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:25\">GEN 32:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:31-Gen32:32\">GEN 32:31–32:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:16\">LEV 26:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:4\">1KI 13:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:18\">2KI 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:5\">2KI 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:18-2Chr21:19\">2CH 21:18–21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:19-2Chr26:21\">2CH 26:19–26:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:20\">LUK 1:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:8\">ACT 9:8</a> <em>Saul's blindness</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:11\">ACT 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:11\">ACT 22:11</a></p>\n<h3>Acts of evil spirits</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:32-Matt9:33\">MAT 9:32–9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17\">MRK 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:25-Mark9:26\">MRK 9:25–9:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:14\">LUK 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:11\">LUK 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a></p>\n<h2>Unfavourable aspects of disability</h2>\n<h3>Unfair advantage taken of the disabled</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:14\">LEV 19:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:26\">2SA 19:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:7\">JHN 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>Disabilities restrict service for God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:16-Lev21:23\">LEV 21:16–21:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:31-2Sam19:37\">2SA 19:31–19:37</a></p>\n<h2>Favourable aspects of disabilities</h2>\n<h3>Prayer to the Lord</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">GEN 25:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:10\">1SA 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27\">MAT 9:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30\">MAT 20:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:32\">MRK 7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:22\">MRK 8:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:8\">2CO 12:8</a></p>\n<h3>Prevention of overconfidence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Proof of God's grace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a></p>\n<h3>Demonstration of God's power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:2-John9:3\">JHN 9:2–9:3</a></p>\n<h2>Disability and God's people</h2>\n<h3>God's blessing may prevent or remove disability</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">GEN 25:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25-Exod23:26\">EXO 23:25–23:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:9\">PSA 113:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:21\">ISA 49:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:1\">ISA 54:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:36\">LUK 1:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:11\">HEB 11:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's providence</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:11\">EXO 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>God protects his servants by disabling their enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:18\">2KI 6:18</a></p>\n<h2>Human attitudes to disabilities</h2>\n<h3>Bitterness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:10\">1SA 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:4\">GEN 16:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:6\">1SA 1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23\">2KI 2:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:5\">PRO 17:5</a></p>\n<h3>Inertness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:6\">JHN 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Rejoicing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:9–12:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's compassion towards those with disabilities</h2>\n<h3>Revealed in the precepts of the law</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:14\">LEV 19:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:18\">DEU 27:18</a></p>\n<h3>Revealed in the promises of the prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16\">ISA 42:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:8\">JER 31:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:6-Mic4:7\">MIC 4:6–4:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:19\">ZEP 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Revealed in the deeds of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:33\">MAT 9:27–9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:29-Matt15:31\">MAT 15:29–15:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:31-Mark7:37\">MRK 7:31–7:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:14\">MAT 21:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:21-Luke7:23\">LUK 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h2>Responsibilities towards those with disabilities</h2>\n<h3>To treat them with respect</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:14\">LEV 19:14</a></p>\n<h3>Not to take advantage of them</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:18\">DEU 27:18</a></p>\n<h3>To provide help for them</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:15\">JOB 29:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:8\">PRO 31:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:13-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:13–14:14</a></p>",
